          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41050307/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41050307/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mijiro/" class=" " title="弥次郎">弥次郎</a>
                (我們不禁要問 你反夶嗎?)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
